name: "Tanks..." Thank You contempo-card
description: "Tanks...For Being An Awesome Dad" contempo-card.  printed on 80# ivory cardstock and comes with premium antique gold envelope! A2 sized.  Or have us print your custom message inside or purchase blank as stationery!

name: Your Friend Royal Rhombus Stationery Set
description: double sided stationery in full sized 8.5" x 11" sheets, 8.5" x 5.5" sheets and 1"x3" return address labels.  Text surface contains watermarked crown and one accent framed corner, and monogramming all printed on high gloss presentation paper.  Reverse side is decorated with a diamond pattern and a large monogram letter of your choice.  More colors coming soon, or request your own theme, whether it's turtles, baby booties and rattles, strawberries, we can do it!  Price listed is for one set of 12 of each piece shown.

name: Pair of Butter-fiti Thank You Cards with Recycled Handmade Paper Butterfly
description: A2 sized pair of cards with textured red palm paper, bohemian butterfly paper and a handmade homemade-paper butterfly with quilled antenna and chenille body-ALL MADE FROM RECYCLED SCRAPS! sexy doesn't have to mean wasteful!  Shown here as a "his and hers" set where one card is not accented with 3D butterfly, and design is made of papers alone.  Included is one premium firecracker red envelope and one premium linen ivory envelope! Price is reduced for a limited time!

name: Mist and Mushrooms Giclee Note Card
description: An original pencil sketch by The Dox artist Michael Morten, turned into a hot little notecard.  Laser printed on 60# cardstock.  Comes with plain white envelopes, but picture shows optional premium metallic copper or tiffany envelope.  Picture features a magical lil dude poking his head out from behind mushrooms. Also available at http://yesumaystationery.etsy.com and http://abreathoffreshstationairy.weebly.com as an "artcard" with no type and white border!  A very interesting look for stationery!  Price Shown is for one set of 8 cards with plain white envelopes.  8 premium envelopes available in your choice of colors for $3.

name: My Paper Has A Mind Of It's Own-Giclee Stationery From The Dox
description: Another original pencil sketch made into stationery from the good doctor Michael Morten. Laser printed onto A2 sized premium "natural" paper and accompanied by "natural" colored envelopes.  Shown here as blank stationery but also available as a notecard with greeting at http://yesumaystationery.etsy.com or http://abreathoffreshstationairy.weebly.com.  Great gift for a guy or a badazz chicka!  Price is for one set of 8 cards with envelopes.
